\begin_layout Standard
We used the conductance based LIF model to model the MBONs.
 The LIF neuron equation is as follows:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\tau_{m}\frac{dV}{dt}=(V_{rest}-V)+g_{ex}(E_{ex}-V)+g_{inh}(E_{inh}-V).
\end{equation}

\end_inset


